definitions.definition: An expression of spite towards someone who suffered a setback .
examples: "The other guy cheated, I had no chance!" " Cope ."

definitions.definition: A contemptuous dismissal , implying that someone should deal with some problem on their own and that the speaker will not engage any further.

main_definition: An expression of spite towards someone who suffered a setback .
secondary_definitions: ( Internet slang ) A contemptuous dismissal , implying that someone should deal with some problem on their own and that the speaker will not engage any further.
